      "body": "Jutros smo mama i ja jeli pekmez sa margarinom.\nU Rumi sam kupio 2 sampite koje smo pojeli kada sam se vratio iz Rume.\nUvece smo mama i ja jeli pohovanu piletinu i grasak.\n",
      "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd\">\n<html><head><meta name=\"qrichtext\" content=\"1\" /><style type=\"text/css\">\np, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }\n</style></head><body style=\" font-family:'Comic Sans MS'; font-size:18px; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;\">\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Jutros smo mama i ja jeli pekmez sa margarinom.</p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">U Rumi sam kupio 2 sampite koje smo pojeli kada sam se vratio iz Rume.</p>\n<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\">Uvece smo mama i ja jeli pohovanu piletinu i grasak.</p>\n<p style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><br /></p></body></html>",
